001package org.nasdanika.common;
002
003import java.util.ArrayList;
004import java.util.List;
005
006public abstract class ListCompoundExecutionParticipant<E extends ExecutionParticipant> extends CompoundExecutionParticipant<E> {
007
008        protected ListCompoundExecutionParticipant(String name) {
009                super(name, false);
010        }
011
012        protected List<E> elements = new ArrayList<>();
013
014        @Override
015        protected List<E> getElements() {
016                return elements;
017        }
018        
019        public void add(E element) {
020                elements.add(element);
021                size = null;
022        }
023
024}
